The '''Thogk''' was a traditional [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorrean]] [[Club/Legends|club]] that literally translated to "log with a spike in it" in [[Gamorrese]]. The Gamorrean males who made a Thogk took great pride in forcing a metal spike into a piece of [[gorgt]] wood with their fists. If a piece of gorgt wood was not available a Gamorrean might make one out of other timber.

The Gamorrean [[Dark Jedi/Legends|Dark Jedi]] [[Gorc]] had a lightsaber that resembled the basic shape of a Thogk.

